cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CV

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and dependency parsing. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it proposes a novel approach for training a parser. Additionally, since the parser is linear-time, it could be relevant to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, since the parser deals with syntactic corpora, it could also be relevant to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as syntactic analysis is often used in image captioning and other computer vision tasks.
